    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/fa3f829db271b98da49efc33b46861c4.webp?t=1757065658\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robes &amp; Wrinkles is a short first-person power-fantasy game placing you in the &quot;Robes&quot; of an evil sorcerer. Taking place within a comically oversized tower, you will face strange warped foes who will be made to cower at your power! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics-Based Tomfoolery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/e4580de4551492be057b5f79d6db5517.poster.avif?t=1757065658\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/e4580de4551492be057b5f79d6db5517.webm?t=1757065658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/e4580de4551492be057b5f79d6db5517.mp4?t=1757065658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The non-serious gameplay allows players to truly immerse themselves as the &quot;Evil Supreme Overlord&quot; they should aspire to be. Smite weaklings with books, tables, barrels (and the literal kitchen sink) to remove the fools from your path...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Dungeons And Handcrafted Short Story Levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/51694352d50f90bfe417fd6684352600.poster.avif?t=1757065658\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/51694352d50f90bfe417fd6684352600.webm?t=1757065658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/51694352d50f90bfe417fd6684352600.mp4?t=1757065658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Play through a short story and then continue with randomly generated dungeons as you collect points to unlock cosmetics and modifiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Cheeky Companion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/13ae4fe9c61baab0255ebdb20f170558.poster.avif?t=1757065658\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/13ae4fe9c61baab0255ebdb20f170558.webm?t=1757065658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144520/extras/13ae4fe9c61baab0255ebdb20f170558.mp4?t=1757065658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You are not alone... Form a pact with your once former minion (...and now &quot;left-hand man&quot;) 'Skully' and use them to channel your powers! Possess objects, cast spells and unleash your ultimate &quot;evilness&quot; against those who oppose your power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What To Expect</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the sake of transparency, you can expect the EA release to contain an initial entry into the Story and an 'Arcade Mode' which features procedural generation. <br><br>Our aim is to provide you with something at launch that can be continuously replayed and we want your feedback to influence our future decisions!  <br><br>We design and develop for fun, if you find something buggy but non game-breaking and funny then make sure to screenshot and show it off! Things will always get fixed and we our keen to share our roadmap soon.</p>",
